WEBVTT

1
00:39:59.820 --> 00:40:02.460 
地球上最古老的生物
The things that live the longest on Earth

2
00:40:02.460 --> 00:40:06.530 
也只不过坚持了地球年龄的百万分之一
endure for only about a millionth of the age of our planet.

3
00:40:06.530 --> 00:40:08.600 
当然 任何一个有机体
So, of course, the individual organisms

4
00:40:08.600 --> 00:40:11.140 
是不可能看到
see nothing of the overall pattern.

5
00:40:11.140 --> 00:40:14.170 
大陆变化的全貌
Of changing continents...

6
00:40:14.170 --> 00:40:16.670 
气候变化的全貌
climate...

7
00:40:16.680 --> 00:40:18.710 
进化的全貌
evolution.

8
00:40:18.710 --> 00:40:21.680 
我们明白 我们的小小起源
That we understand even a little of our origins

9
00:40:21.680 --> 00:40:25.950 
都是人类洞察和勇气的伟大胜利之一
is one of the great triumphs of human insight and courage.

10
00:40:25.950 --> 00:40:29.720 
我们是谁 我们怎么来到这里
Who we are and why we are here can only be glimpsed

11
00:40:29.720 --> 00:40:32.660 
答案只能通过拼凑零星的碎片获得
by piecing together something of the full picture,

